title: Pinkpop 2013
description:
Pinkpop 2013
============

Coverage of the 2013 edition of Pinkpop Festival. None of the headliners (The Killers, Kings of Leon, Green Day) gave permission
for live broadcast but for the Kings of Leon are highlights available.


Besides complete performances and highlights, I've also included various '3 On Stage' sessions (see below for more details) made
by various Dutch and international artists.


All footage were taken from the livestream and the image quality is acceptable if you don't have any high definition expectations.


Video: 710x400/25fps
Audio: Stereo @ 44.1 kHz/128Kb per second
